data("heart")
# cleaning a bit of the `heart` data
heart2 <- heart %>% 
  as_tibble(heart) %>% 
  mutate(family_history = ifelse(famhist==1, "Yes", "No"),
         heart_disease = ifelse(y==1, "Yes", "No"))
